Status Definitions

✅ Accepted: Decision has been approved and implemented
🔄 Proposed: Decision is under review
⏸️ Deprecated: Decision has been superseded
❌ Rejected: Decision was not approved

Creating New ADRs
When adding a new ADR:

Copy the template
Number it sequentially (e.g., 011-new-decision.md)
Fill in all sections
Submit for review via Pull Request
Update this index

